Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bermimpi buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Adikku, Akari, meninggal di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menjadi hantu dan keluar dari ponselku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.55,0:00:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu orang mesum berbaju hitam muncul,\Nmengaku sebagai pembasmi roh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya, aku membangkitkan\Nkekuatanku dan mengalahkan Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mimpi yang konyol.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamar hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah itu hanya mimpi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana mungkin itu mimpi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana mungkin ini mimpi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempat apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini hotel cinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kau lakukan padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hotel cinta?\NMemang ini Era Showa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akari…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Adikku, setelah kejadian itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu ponselmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baterainya sudah terisi penuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akari…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akun gaib
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah hantu dari akun media sosial\Nyang sudah mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Usai pembasmian roh,\Nakun itu akan hilang sepenuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa kirim pesan lagi padanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, dia sudah lama meninggal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia meninggal karena sakit,\Njadi kurasa sudah waktunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dan adikku sudah berjanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski sendirian,\Naku harus hidup dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika terus menangis,\Nbukankah aku melanggar janji?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena sudah di hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bagaimana jika mandi sebelum kembali?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar sampah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf. Itu kejam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh menjijikkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jelas sekali senyummu dipaksakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kau yang menyuruhku\Nberadaptasi dan jalani hidupku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasubata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku Kukuru Kasubata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan panggil nama depanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ikut aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuantar kau ke pemandian umum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, hotel ini tampak sangat mewah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini Akademi Miden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sekolah untuk medium roh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekolah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini jelas hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu ruangan tadi…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tata letak dengan ruang\Ndi dekat jendela itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kamar pribadiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, ini sekolah asrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Konon dirancang sebagai penginapan onsen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk melambangkan pembasmian roh\Ndan membawa keberuntungan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Aoringo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia MyuTuber yang viral karena kontroversi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada yang indah dari videonya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar kemampuannya bangkit semalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasubata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar kau mengacau?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak menduga dia akan membuat kesalahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:05:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia selalu sombong,\Ntapi hanya itu yang bisa dia lakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu, Kusaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasubata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasihan. Aku ingin menghiburnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kusaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang kasar\Nyang hidup dari memancing hujatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beraninya dia masuk akademi ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, aku juga suka\Nmemancing hujatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria berambut biru itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tampak keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kusaba…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasubata juga hebat, tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Judulnya
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Aoringo Busuk".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tidak ada yang indah dari itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga berlangganan kanal Aoringo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menonton videonya sangat menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang berbahaya yang videonya\Nselalu menyebabkan kontroversi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah, aku enggan berurusan dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Azaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau kau apakan dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terserah apa yang akan guru itu lakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemampuannya sama dengan pria itu. Jijik.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempat apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kusatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini benar-benar hotel, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini ruang rekreasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini benar-benar hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini toko suvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini hotel onsen, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manju itu tampak lezat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini onsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, ini hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lukaku sudah sembuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hangat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, setelah tubuhku hangat,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku ingin menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke mana biksu bodoh itu pergi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biksu Laut telah tiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:07:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terkejut dengan kejutan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan di akademi bagi medium roh,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biksu Laut tidak akan muncul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi profesiku biksu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Pak Azaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau tiba-tiba berdiri dari air panas,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pembuluh darahmu akan membesar\Ndan kau bisa anemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu berbahaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku akan anemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar-benar mengejutkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, terima kasih sudah ikut bermain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Azaki, guru di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Guru, sesuai instruksi,\Naku sudah mengajaknya berkeliling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasubata,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jangan terlihat seperti sedang dihukum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika bukan hukuman, lalu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pembasmi roh berapi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mau bersamanya sedetik pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu dia punya Api Biru Langit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:07:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pendapatmu tentang akademi kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Onsen di sini luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat nikmat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong pakai bajumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau setuju mendaftar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enishiro, jadilah medium roh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kejutan lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Azaki, ini lelucon, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu itu ditujukan padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama sekali tidak.\NWajar jika merekrut murid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia telah membangkitkan\Nsiberkinesis miliknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siberkinesis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, bukan?\NKau tidak penasaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kuceritakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ceritanya panjang.\NKau tidak keberatan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak zaman kuno,\Nprofesi medium roh telah ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama ribuan tahun,\Nmereka bertarung melawan roh jahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama bertahun-tahun,\Nmedium roh menggunakan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:09:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}metode pelepasan energi spiritual\Nyang disebut "psikokinesis".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi beberapa dekade terakhir,\Nkeadaan berubah drastis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan munculnya internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}obsesi orang mati\Ntelah bergeser di internet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan wujud hantu berubah bersamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat itulah medium roh menjadi gelisah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menghadapi entitas\Nyang dikenal sebagai "akun gaib"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}psikokinesis yang mereka kembangkan\Nturun-temurun tidak berguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dunia medium roh yang konservatif\Nterpaksa berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya, teknologi pengubah\Nkekuatan spiritual menjadi digital
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}melalui perangkat elektronik lahir.\NItu disebut "siberkinesis".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kusatsu…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu di Prefektur Gunma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yubatake? Aku harus memeriksanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau jahat sekali! Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kita baru saja akrab?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang kau mencairkan suasana untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak ingin tahu\Napa yang terjadi padamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku sama sekali tidak tertarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak lagi terlibat dengan hantu\Natau medium roh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tidak peduli dengan siberkinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mau menjadi medium roh\Natau streamer pemancing hujatan lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin bekerja dengan rajin,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}makan satu pencuci mulut\Ndalam sehari, dan tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah kehidupan yang ingin kujalani.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andai Akari bisa membaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemikiran itu segalanya bagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kini tidak ada yang tersisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang ada hanyalah diriku yang kosong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu saja. Selamat tinggal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membeli manju di toko\Nsebelum pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manju.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa? Kau sungguh akan pulang?\N- Manju…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Adikmu sudah meninggal.\N- Manju…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kau bahkan tak tanya alasannya?\N- Manju…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya kau tertarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Adikmu bukan meninggal karena sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia dibunuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:11:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pembunuhnya adalah akun gaib yang kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak Soji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak Soji, aku tak bisa bernapas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamatkan aku…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akun gaib itu mengincar mereka\Nyang punya ikatan kuat dengan dunia ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu semua korbannya\Nmeneteskan air mata darah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Adikmu juga begitu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana pria itu sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau bertanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa? Bukankah sudah jelas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membunuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kau lemah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Minggir, Kasubata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menghajar biksu tersenyum itu\Nsampai dia mengatakan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biksu itu mungkin punya wajah tersenyum\Nyang tak seharusnya dimiliki biksu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia tetap wali kelas kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah, panggil aku "berseri-seri".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari bermain, Enishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau bisa mengalahkan Kasubata,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan kuakui kekuatanmu\Ndan mengatakan semua yang kuketahui.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu jika kau bisa melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aktifkan siber.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa jika dia dihabisi, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasubata yang akan melawanmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan konyol!\NAku tidak mau bermain denganmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Adikku sudah meninggal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bersikap sok penting\Ndan memamerkan kemalanganmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hal seperti itu sudah biasa di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menghajar Enishiro si berengsek ini\Nterasa menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini lebih menegangkan\Ndaripada melawan adikmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Biksu Bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:13:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat aku menghabisi pria ini,\Nsebaiknya kau ceritakan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, sepertinya ada pertunjukan di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Murid kelas satu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak berambut biru itu,\Naku belum pernah melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingat dia cukup terkenal, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Azaki, kenapa berisik sekali di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakiko, kau di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau ingin bertarung,\Nlakukan di ruang latihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian semua,\Nbuka mata dan perhatikan baik-baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasakan ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang satu menyerang\Ndan yang lain mengompori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertarungan ini\Ncuma kumpulan sampah internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kiyomi, apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jarang sekali melihat Aoringo bertarung.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sangat langka, mengerti?\NHabisi dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jarang sekali seseorang\Nberhadapan dengan Kukuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hasu-Hasu, kirimkan videomu nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, mereka tidak boleh berkelahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong hentikan mereka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial! Panjang palunya terus berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu Itabashi, ada apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Nanzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Azaki membiarkan anak\Nyang dia bawa semalam melawan Kasubata…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepala Sekolah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepala Sekolah,\Nkita harus segera menghentikan mereka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurut laporan, anak itu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}harus disingkirkan secepatnya…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini, aku tak mengincar ponselmu.\NAku mengincarmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima pukulan lagi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan biarkan aku bersenang-senang,\Npemancing hujatan sialan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhentilah mengatakan "pemancing hujatan".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak berniat jadi pemancing hujatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya butuh dana\Nuntuk menyembuhkan adikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitukah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga punya adik laki-laki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa memahami perasaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu dia. "Keluarga yang sakit"\Nadalah alasan yang bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pikir bisa berbuat sesukamu dengan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasubata…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukuru selalu seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepribadian yang buruk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat siapa yang bicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau butuh uang,\Nada cara lain mendapatkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akui saja kau menikmatinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak pernah puas\Nmenjadi pusat perhatian.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya,\Nkau membangkitkan api semacam itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seberapa jauh kau akan mendorongku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar berengsek!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.\NAku menggunakan kata yang tidak pantas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kekuatan macam apa ini?\NItu curang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mengerti sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini "siberkinesis".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sehebat apa pun kau bertarung,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau tidak bisa melawannya\Nhanya dengan tubuhmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau juga harus mencoba\Nmenggunakan siberkinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini, ambil media penyalurnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penyalur?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ponselmu. Itu pengubah psikokinesismu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu kau bangkit, tubuhmu secara alami\Nakan ingat cara menggunakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bayangkan perlahan\Nmemusatkan panas di perutmu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ke tangan yang memegang ponsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Warna itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pembasmi roh api? Tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Api Biru Langit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku terkejut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Awalnya aku ragu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi itu jelas…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Api Hantu".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Api Hantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Api Hantu, api biru langit\Nyang seperti ular.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Api Hantu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasubata, kau mengerti, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sentuh apinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana reaksi semua orang?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini buruk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, seseorang memiliki\Nkemampuan yang sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan cemaskan itu sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bagaimana perasaanmu sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apinya tidak panas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, terasa sangat nyaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, tunjukkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemampuan Api Hantu-mu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Api yang dipindahkan akan segera padam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa aku berpikir\Nuntuk membalut kakiku dengan api?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tahu itu tindakan yang tepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengalirkan api ke kedua kaki sekaligus…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemampuan ini\Nbenar-benar terkesan perang online.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ledakan yang memperkuat\Nbagian tubuh yang terbakar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penguatan Api!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, bukankah kemampuannya\Nbaru bangkit kemarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo! Kalahkan dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisi maniak PC itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini gawat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukuru sudah dibutakan oleh amarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana menurutmu, Kakiko?\NDia hebat, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memiliki bakat murni untuk kekerasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan saatnya berkomentar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong hentikan mereka, Pak Azaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, aku sudah melihat\Nyang ingin kulihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas kerja keras kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam! Jangan menghalangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar perjaka sialan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku seorang biksu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, aku mempraktikkan asketisme.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku tak malu dengan kesucianku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tak ada hubungannya\Ndengan aku populer atau tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Azaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, menilai seseorang\Ndari pengalaman seksual mereka,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukankah itu nilai kuno yang kalian benci?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setidaknya, begitulah menurutku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat. Aku terlalu kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kekuatan ini, aku tak terkalahkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, aku akan membuat\NKasubata meminta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak akan lolos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah itu akun gaib atau apa pun,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan kuhabisi mereka semua!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Civility Pile-On!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kuat sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lemah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasubata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau agak berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Secara fisik dan verbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kau tak menyakitiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tidak cukup untuk menyakitiku…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau jelas hampir mengalami\Nkekalutan mental.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menghentikan palu besar itu sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu gila.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, Enishiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Izinkan aku meminta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membiarkan sosok itu lolos\Ndan gagal menghentikan kematian adikmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan memprovokasimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya ingin memancingmu melepaskan\Nsiberkinesismu demi memastikan kekuatanmu…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku yang harus minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh minta maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mendaftar, Pak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah itu medium roh atau apa pun,\Naku akan menerimanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itulah…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan jadi lebih kuat di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih kuat dari siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enishiro, dirimu yang sekarang,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jauh lebih baik daripada senyummu\Nyang dipaksakan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat aku cukup kuat,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan membalaskan dendam Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang di Akademi Miden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan, manju onsen kami yang lezat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Api Hantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa terima siapa pun\Nyang menguasai kekuatan Api Hantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:21:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini dari Kepala Sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya ini biaya perbaikan\Nkerusakan sekolah.
